bibl.title: Fragment of pottery from the table of a Prefect of Egypt?
bibl.seg: Adam Łukaszewicz, Fragment of Pottery from the Table of a Prefect of Egypt?
Fragment of pottery with a graffiti (Ἰοῦλις Ἰουλιανό[ς], prefect in 314?) found in sector F of the area excavated at Kom el-Dikka by the Polish mission of the University of Warsaw.
